column5: Nice! Do you put any weight above the lure?  I have the same color and size.  Never caught anything on it  . Maybe I have to try harder  I did catch a bass on the bleeding frog flatfish.
Nice. My go to bait as well.
Such a good outing now u gotta stock up on some more kwikfish eh

Nice! Do you put any weight above the lure?  I have the same color and size.  Never caught anything on it  . Maybe I have to try harder  I did catch a bass on the bleeding frog flatfish.  I don't add any weight.  I tie straight to my mainline and cast with a slow retrieve.  Nice. My go to bait as well.  I wanna try catching a steelhead next  Such a good outing now u gotta stock up on some more kwikfish eh  That fish stole my firetiger and I got my Silver/green UV hung on the bottom.  So many colours I wanna buy now
